graph TD
    ATM[ATM Machine] --> L2[L2 Switch]
    L2 --> L3[L3 Switch]
    L3 --> Core[Core L3 Switch]
    
    Core --> ACL{Access Control List}
    
    ACL -- Permit VLAN 50 --> SVR[(Transaction Server)]
    ACL -- Block --> Internal[Other Internal VLANs]
    ACL -- Block --> Web[Internet]

    style ACL fill:#ff9,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style SVR fill:#9f9,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Internal fill:#f99,stroke:#333
    style Web fill:#f99,stroke:#333


graph TD
